async function query() {
  const { page, sort, filters } = $data
  const { time = [] } = filters
  const begin = time[0] ? `${time[0]}+00:00:00` : undefined
  const end = time[1] ? `${time[1]}+23:59:59` : undefined
  const params = Object.assign({ 
  	flowCode: 'a2f852f6dcca48cfa7826ffb1129d040',
    userCode: $info.userInfo.userCode,
    creatorCode: filters.creatorCode,
    ['beginTime']: begin,
    ['endTime']: end,
    flowOptName: filters.flowOptName,
  }, page, sort)
  $data.loading = true
  const {
  	objList,
    pageDesc,
  } = await $dde.get('f267ad9a50c64300b1f1c1a6c38f780f', { params }) 
  $data.page = pageDesc
  $data.list = objList
  $data.loading = false
}
